<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #fce4ec;
            color: #880e4f;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin: 0;
        }
        h1 { color: #d81b60; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        .card {
            background: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
            max-width: 720px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .label {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #fce7f3;
            color: #9d174d;
            border: 1px solid #fbcfe8;
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 4px 14px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .time-box {
            background: #fff0f6;
            border: 1px solid #f9a8d4;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            margin: 1.2rem 0;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }
        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }
        .nav-links a {
            background: #ec4899;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .nav-links a:hover { background: #be185d; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="label">⚙️ Server-Side Rendered — EJS Template</div>
        <h1><%= title %> — EJS Template</h1>
        <p>This page is <strong>dynamically rendered</strong> by Express using the EJS view engine.</p>
        <p>The same data is also available as a JSON API at <code>/api/dynamic</code> for React and Angular to consume.</p>
        <div class="time-box">
            🕐 Server Time: <strong><%= serverTime %></strong>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="/">⬅ Vanilla JS Board</a>
            <a href="http://localhost:5173/ejs-demo" target="_blank">⚛ React App — EJS Demo</a>
            <a href="http://localhost:4200" target="_blank">🅰 Angular App — EJS Demo</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
